    <h3 class="faq-header">What vaccination rate is needed for HPV herd immunity?</h3>
    <div class="faq-content">
      <p>Models suggest that achieving high vaccination coverage (typically 70-80% of both males and females) is needed to establish strong herd immunity against targeted HPV types.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
